{"tid":907860,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"屢遭義工遞五星旗干擾 中國馬拉松跑手「失金」","createTime":"2018-11-19T07:00:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-19T14:45:15.000Z","uid":38172,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"a15fed6b378f51d71e123b9df63b3ecd33c9b00b","tid":907860,"uid":38172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T07:00:34.000Z","msg":"江蘇蘇州國際馬拉松比賽於周日（18日）舉行，中國選手何引麗失卻金牌，但讓她落敗的不是來自肯尼亞的勁敵，而是因為在比賽途中屢遭義工闖入跑道，要求她接過手上的五星紅旗，致使其跑步節奏受到干擾，最終以5秒之差屈居亞軍。事件隨後成為網民熱話，並紛紛留言怒罵涉事義工「腦子進水了吧」、「氣死人了」。<br />\n<br />\n從比賽畫面可見，當賽事進入最後500米時，何引麗與肯尼亞選手在跑道上互不相讓，突然場邊一名義工向何遞上旗幟，她未有理會繼續跑；不料隨後又有另一名義工又遞上五星紅旗，何無奈下接過旗幟，但2次干擾，令其被對手拉開距離，最終失去奪金機會。<br />\n<br />\n內地媒體指出，馬拉松是一項耗時長、對體力消耗巨大的運動，在最後衝刺階段，跑手恨不得身上甚麼都沒有，此時哪怕是一毫克的重量都是負擔，接旗亦會造成分神和瞬時降速，或許是她未能奪冠的原因。報道又指，即使要讓運動員手持旗幟，也應該是在通過終點或頒獎之時，在比賽還在進行時遞旗，不但影響體育賽場秩序，亦干擾運動員的競技狀態，主辦方亦應作檢討。<br />\n<br />\n事件鬧得滿城風雨，兩名義工及主辦方都被網民怒轟。主辦方蘇州高新區體育局回應稱，官方原則上不允許其他人進入賽道，這屬於義工的個人行為，但他們認為「不應該追究某個人的責任」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20181119/bkn-20181119110622460-1119_00952_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20181119%2Fbkn-20181119110622460-1119_00952_001.html&d=1qQUYiz6aatzlv%2BlB%2BK4%2Fr%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=6e8e9973\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20181119/bkn-20181119110622460-1119_00952_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20181119/photo/bkn-20181119110622460-1119_00952_001_03b.jpg?20181119142555\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20181119%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181119110622460-1119_00952_001_03b.jpg%3F20181119142555&h=65bdf680&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b3eec838902baf4422d440c79b9e57a6fb8570d1","tid":907860,"uid":48222,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T07:04:41.000Z","msg":"豬隊友<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71dda6e76af723a532c011d04610e05d1836be46","tid":907860,"uid":68008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T07:10:50.000Z","msg":"肯尼亞條女陰陰嘴笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7726d537653d454686172d436c31ae25fae0eba1","tid":907860,"uid":19126,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T07:13:01.000Z","msg":"做得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e2afc172a0d99052e850f95bb655bd9c228b357","tid":907860,"uid":119028,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T07:13:11.000Z","msg":"中國人應該罵個跑手才對<br />\n接個國旗要幾秒 咁都唔接<br />\n 對得起中國人嗎？"},{"pid":"f640a01b8b944d9708e9276acfb5ab2b07393869","tid":907860,"uid":70439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T07:16:26.000Z","msg":"沒事兒"},{"pid":"cc6120ea01b5774c55f791eaa00f335f810cf92f","tid":907860,"uid":82720,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T07:18:27.000Z","msg":"佢有接到國旗架 跑咗幾步覺得唔對路掟落地<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n事後仲要出post解釋係跣手<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc684087bf70dfbaf1ab394d8e5ad6e749d01a0d","tid":907860,"uid":45830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T07:24:30.000Z","msg":"戇鳩有樣睇。。。"},{"pid":"47c04b048d6f0d3be0ac62a39742c6bab3a90852","tid":907860,"uid":170942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T07:28:13.000Z","msg":"唔接又唔撚得，搞到成國玻璃碎點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n#一點都不能少<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10dac7d23c2b29c9e5f2c0a2e638d3c0ac2d699e","tid":907860,"u